title.rendered: Paket CCTV Omniview 16 Channel Ultimate HDTVI

content.rendered: Tingkatkan sistem keamanan bangunan dengan memasang Omniview Paket CCTV Omniview 16 Channel Ultimate HDTVI. Kamera CCTV Omniview dapat menangkap gambar video bahkan dalam kondisi cahaya yang minim. Jenis kamera Omniview type Paket CCTV Omniview 16 Channel Ultimate HDTVI memiliki spesifikasi, yaitu: > Jumlah CCTV 8 Unit > Tipe CCTV CCTV Camera Omniview OMN-IAT130 > Resolusi CCTV 1.3 MP > Image Sensor 1/3” Sensor Resolution 960P Lens 3.6mm > Infrared Range IR Distance up to 30m IR > Tipe DVR CCTV DVR Omniview OMV-S04N > Fitur 08 Ch 1080N AHD DVR > Video Output Support VGA,HDMI HD Output > Audio In 8x Audio in / 1x Audio Out > Harddisk Support 1 HDD SATA up to 3 TB > Recording Resolution 8 Ch 1080N real-time
